Hello webflow devs ðŸ‘‹

This extension was created because I hated waiting for that long page load with global code to insert a local project script (<script src="http://localhost:5137/main.js"></script>).

So, what does this extension do?

First of all it loads and removes the script very fast, you can do it manually or by shortcuts (Shift + + [Add dev link] and Shift + - [Remove dev link]).

By default I use vite to create a local project, so port 5137 and main.js file for the entry point. But this can be changed in the settings if you click on the icon that appears in the menu in designer mode in webflow.
